==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From  [[ῥύομαι]] {{GG|4506}} in the sense of its congener   [[ῥέω]] {{GG|4482}}; 

===Pronunciation===
ῥύσις / rhusis / hroo'-sis

===Noun===
'''ῥύσις'''

# a flux (of blood): - [[issue]].

